{
  "stem": "2004.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Of course, I have given some of it to him, because, first of all, he was a very nice person.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was a nice man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, of course, I believed that he is instrumental in securing food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He is entitled to get a certain part of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he's gotten the best deal for me, under the circumstances at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I have also made sure that any time I'm needed outside, I should be the one to select bedding.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because this has now become a sort of a gold mine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "After all, you select bedding, there is a very good possibility that you will find gold coins in those bedding.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Also, I might add, a friend of mine found a gold-- a gold coin in some of the clothing, in sleeves, gold coins.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In Poland, they used to make jackets and suits which had padded shoulders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, the first thing they looked for, I mean, our friends, they looked in the padding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was a possibility that there might be a gold coin in the padding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Also, the people that were working in shoes, they were trying to see if they-- to rip off the sole from shoes, because it is a good possibility that there might be coins in-- there were double soles.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And some of the coins-- some of the shoes, basically, were-- were-- were constructed so to hide coins.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had shoemakers in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they-- and they were able to construct shoes which had double sole with some space in between, whereby you could hide valuables.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Unfortunately, as it later turned out to be, when you did get to a concentration camp, all your clothing was taken away from you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So whatever you had in your shoes or otherwise was gone, anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
